    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it's time for someone else to enjoy this absolute dream of a car! It has been totally babied since day one and is in truly incredible, like-new condition. I\u2019ve kept it spotless inside and out\u2014honestly, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 42900.0,
