    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning collector is a 1994 Mazda RX-7 (FD3S) in flawless condition. This example is powered by the iconic 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, which maintains factory-spec compression and a leak-free vacuum system. The drivetrain features a precise 5-speed short-throw manual transmission paired with a Torsen limited-slip differential. Its lightweight chassis retains the original aluminum double-wishbone suspension, providing the razor-sharp handling and 50/50 weight distribution these cars are legendary for. The exterior finish is showroom-quality, with no signs of paint degradation or structural fatigue. Inside, the cockpit is immaculate, featuring pristine bolsters and original instrumentation. Mechanically unmolested and fully documented, this FD represents a rare opportunity to own a quintessential 90s performance icon in its purest form.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
