    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting an absolutely pristine 2018 BMW M3, a vehicle that transcends the 'used' label to offer a showroom-fresh experience. This enthusiast-owned masterpiece has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a drop of rain. The Alpine White paint is flawless, treated with a professional-grade ceramic coating that provides a deep, liquid-like luster. Inside, the Sakhir Orange Extended Merino Leather remains supple and unmarked, with zero wear on the bolsters and a cabin that still carries the factory-new aroma. Every service milestone was met early at a certified BMW center, and the car comes with a comprehensive history folder. From the untouched 19-inch forged wheels to the pristine carbon-fiber roof, every inch of this car reflects a life of pampered care. This is a rare opportunity to own a modern legend in truly concours-level condition.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
