    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've absolutely got to see this beauty. It's in stunning, showroom-level condition and has been treated like total royalty\u2014honestly, it's like it just rolled off the lot! Not a single scratch or dent to be found, and it still has that fresh feel and drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for total perfection, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
