    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in concours-ready condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The mechanical synchronization is flawless; the dual-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled with upgraded seals, and the rear subframe has undergone proactive reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. Finished in Titanium Silver over Black Nappa leather, the factory paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the underside remains free of oxidation. Equipped with the M-Variable Differential Lock and perfectly calibrated suspension geometry, this M3 provides the visceral, analog feedback sought by purists. Complete documentation confirms a lifetime of rigorous preventative maintenance.",
